data.name: lb_AboutDescription.Text
data.value: Controller Service provides gyroscope and accelerometer support to the AYA NEO 2020 and 2021 models through a virtual DualShock 4 or Xbox 360 controller. If the service is enabled, embedded controller will be cloaked to applications outside the whitelist. If the service is disabled, embedded controller will be uncloaked and virtual controller disabled. Controller Service relies on ViGEmBus driver and ViGEmClient libraries as well as HidHide kernel-mode filter driver. Therefore, we strongly encourage you in donating to Nefarius via PayPal for continued maintenance and development.
